{"tid":2230864,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔睇算命結果住，會唔會證明到人覺得算命準唔準","createTime":"2020-10-05T08:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T05:13:04.000Z","uid":246648,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e3dd3ffb54478995a1561f1a86062ec3cdae6758","tid":2230864,"uid":246648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T08:37:26.000Z","msg":"例如搵個算命佬，算10年20年，但係個結果錄音收埋唔比算命對象知<br />\n<br />\n過10年20年攞返出黎聽<br />\n<br />\n咁就唔會有心理作用<br />\n<br />\n如是者實驗200組人<br />\n<br />\n100組比結果，另外100組唔比結果<br />\n<br />\n10年後做份問卷睇下佢地覺得準唔準<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意返係<span class=\"red\">人覺得</span>算命準唔準，而唔係算命本身準唔準<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PB2f87E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPB2f87E.jpg&h=bf1e0c1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"929528c211dfe35356c0e58fbc22959d20c5048e","tid":2230864,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T08:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DvS70gc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDvS70gc.gif&h=3a49f14d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ba09be73e323f1dfe656db514074e6a76947c7e","tid":2230864,"uid":104217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"直接算你既過去咪得"}]}